Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 很危險 牽著手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都不是那個年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該互相依賴畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健 小雪 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和姐 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 還是老樣子笨手笨腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好過份 哪有人這樣子講青梅竹馬的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 你應該對人家溫柔點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 對她太好不會有好下場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 小健
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 麻美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 健次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 哥哥 日和姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見囉 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早 健次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早 南山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你趕快把黃書還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南山 清香 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 日和 還有附帶的健次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早 態度傲慢的小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 妳怎麼能夠一早就跟這種自大的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就是你的累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒把他視為累贅啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 我才是背負重擔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 淨會耍嘴皮子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進籐同學 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了 我看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天妳又跟哥哥一起上學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像一大早就跟情人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們相依偎的樣子 太令人羨慕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才不是…情人呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 你們不是沒血緣關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你們可以結婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼浪漫而戲劇化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多好啊 兩人的熱情擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣了 進籐同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛呀 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想吃 小健 跟我換菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你嘛 嗚嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 要吃哪個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想要交換
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是妳做的便當嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的菜一樣 為什麼要換
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦 就挑妳喜歡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人節快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 妳每年都送巧克力給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親手做不是很累嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會 因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只需要做一個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳看 是玩具球機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:07:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真懷念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候我們常買呢 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 趕快回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕一個人呆在房間 嚇得哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後哥哥就敲另一邊的牆壁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那以後我就不怕晚上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那時候起 我一直暗戀著哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…我沒有資格開口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:09:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健 早上了 快起床
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我再睡一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣 小健
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我就很想問了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼妳們要輪流換人來叫醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們商量好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是問為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡替換到這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的考試準備得怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經這麼晚了 第五測驗還是無法做完…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就住下來吧 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪的胸部好軟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和姐 好癢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管 我幫妳洗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好癢的 怎樣怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次換我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼上鎖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我們常一起洗澡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪妳還記得嗎？未來的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來的夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國小時候的那個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的夢想是當小健的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.90,0:11:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡白馬王子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而那個王子就是小健呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今夢想依然沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿日和沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說要唸書到早上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果最先睡的卻是她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個青梅竹馬太軟弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥喜歡日和姐吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡日和？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟她在一起的時候很高興的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 是她太需要人照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相較之下妳就能幹多了 我也輕鬆多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是好妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次考試 應該可以避免不及格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 是我有實力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我住在你家教你的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳明明在睡大覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 遊樂園已經建好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去坐咖啡杯耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就明天去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學校放假 正好可以紀念考試結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贊成 那麼要選在幾點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛…我怕太晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和姐…對不起… 我不該打擾你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要撞上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 小健
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是順手而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好失敗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:14:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪跟日和不同 很能幹 我還以為沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找不到材料 就出來買了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等著看吧 今年的巧克力很用心的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你碰到日和姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是她每年送的巧克力 都做得很難吃 也難看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到今年我才注意到 她是很努力在做巧克力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 情人節是明天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我很忙 沒時間給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忙到沒時間給我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有守約定…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明約好要輪流給的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我卻提前送給哥哥 這麼做 又不可能成為情侶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個戒指並不屬於我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥如果知道 一定會討厭我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 就算當妹妹也好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當妹妹也好 我希望哥哥喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健 給你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辦不到 辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法看著這樣子的哥哥露出笑容…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪昨天把巧克力送給你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪怎麼先…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健 回去吧 小雪一定在等著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪的感受我注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然也有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健 我有重要的事跟你談
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳先到房間去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體不舒服 在睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望她早點恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 妳的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做的巧克力不好吃 我想還是別讓你吃比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 明年起我就不做巧克力了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健 如果我不在的話你會寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳怎麼說這個 日和 妳很奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我 小健
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂妳話中的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓小雪找回笑容的只有小健哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從以前到現在我一直當成親妹妹保護的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是這個妹妹卻把我當成男人來愛慕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直把小雪當成一個女人看待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只因為她是妹妹 就潛意識的壓抑自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 到我的房間來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥送我的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來應該交給日和姐的戒指…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我一直說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我幫日和姐保管一個玩具戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是哥哥贏到玩具球 送她的藍色戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太高興就忘記自己是幫日和姐保管
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一直不敢跟日和姐開口提起戒指的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實那是日和姐的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天 我都不敢跟她走在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:22:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撒謊說三人一排一起走路會妨礙到別人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和姐知道後就說 那我們每天輪流找哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那以後 做什麼事我們都輪流了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於對日和姐開口說了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當我全部說出 道歉時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.70,0:22:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和姐說 姐姐的白馬王子不是哥哥你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.30,0:22:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是為了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和姐的心情明明跟我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那時間我卻很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.50,0:22:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是壞女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從很久很久以前開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.40,0:22:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以留在哥哥的身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪不在身邊我會困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.20,0:23:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.80,0:23:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好難為情哦 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.50,0:23:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.50,0:23:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.10,0:24:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.20,0:24:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.80,0:24:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.50,0:24:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.10,0:24:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以把自己全部交給哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.00,0:24:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來了 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.80,0:24:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.60,0:24:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事 可以忍到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.80,0:24:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.50,0:25:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.60,0:25:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.50,0:25:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.00,0:25:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不想離開哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.80,0:25:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.40,0:26:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.80,0:26:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戒指還給妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.40,0:26:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.50,0:26:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我早點看到你像個男人的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.20,0:26:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.60,0:26:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.10,0:26:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.50,0:26:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.30,0:27:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得戒指膩了再給我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.70,0:27:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和姐
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.20,0:27:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別吃驚哦 健次
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.50,0:27:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和轉學了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.60,0:27:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和轉學？真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.90,0:27:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我這個好友都不通知
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.30,0:28:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她應該先講一聲的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.80,0:28:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.10,0:28:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了我與小雪 強顏歡笑默默離開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.90,0:28:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.20,0:28:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,--  『こころのカケラ』  作词: 佐藤裕美  作曲编曲: 藤间仁  歌: 佐藤裕美  --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.62,0:29:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnZhunYuan\fs18\fad(300,300)\blur1\3c&H966464&\b0}心の欠片　探すよに　君の事　探し続けてた
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.74,0:29:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnZhunYuan\fs18\fad(300,300)\blur1\3c&H966464&\b0}モノクロの　毎日が　君がいて   輝き始めてく
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.40,0:29:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnZhunYuan\fs18\fad(300,300)\blur1\3c&H966464&\b0}壊してしまう怖さに立ち向かう勇気をくれたね
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.18,0:30:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnZhunYuan\fs18\fad(300,300)\blur1\3c&H966464&\b0}未来の窓   開ける強さを
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.22,0:30:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnZhunYuan\fs18\fad(300,300)\blur1\3c&H966464&\b0}君が好き　ただそれだけで　迷わず行けるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.08,0:30:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnZhunYuan\fs18\fad(300,300)\blur1\3c&H966464&\b0}水色綺麗な空の　下をいつまで
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.36,0:30:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnZhunYuan\fs18\fad(300,300)\blur1\3c&H966464&\b0}君と歩いてく　この道をずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.00,0:31:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜歡的小雪與小健
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.30,0:31:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你們以後可以永遠和好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.20,0:31:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是但是但是 我從很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.40,0:31:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就喜歡小健是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.90,0:31:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我轉學了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.00,0:31:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.90,0:31:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水色 第二期 〜日和之章〜
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.20,0:31:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜待佳音哦
